230
00:16:12,430 --> 00:16:14,280
sampai kau menunda pertemuan
dengan Presdir.

231
00:16:40,950 --> 00:16:42,130
Yeo Jun-wan dan

232
00:16:43,230 --> 00:16:44,380
Yeo Jun.

233
00:16:44,730 --> 00:16:46,230
Bagaimana denganmu? Punya saudara?

234
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,570
Tidak, aku anak tunggal.

235
00:16:59,340 --> 00:17:01,270
Kenapa tadi tidak menyapa?
Kau melihatku, bukan?

236
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:04,790
Kau menonjol ke mana pun kau pergi.

237
00:17:06,109 --> 00:17:09,060
Apa aku begitu menyilaukan?
Aku bersinar terang seperti berlian?

238
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:12,230
Artinya kau bisa menemukanku di mana pun.

239
00:17:13,859 --> 00:17:14,960
Benar.

240
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:18,569
Aku menatapmu karena mau bilang sesuatu.

241
00:17:20,550 --> 00:17:23,230
Akan kujawab pertanyaanmu tempo hari.

242
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:24,640
Tunggu sebentar.

243
00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:27,630
Biarkan aku bersiap.

244
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:33,480
Silakan.

245
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,610
Terima kasih sudah menyatakan perasaanmu.

246
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:38,980
Tapi...

247
00:17:40,430 --> 00:17:41,840
Aku tetap pada pendirianku

248
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:45,540
tentang tidak mengenalmu
dan takut kepadamu.

249
00:17:47,870 --> 00:17:49,370
Kau mau mengenalku?

250
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,390
Kau mau.

251
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:00,100
Sedikit.

252
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:01,990
Begini...

253
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:05,340
Hanya karena aku orang yang penasaran.

254
00:18:06,260 --> 00:18:07,710
Bukan karena aku menyukaimu.

255
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:09,910
Biar kuperjelas soal itu.

