338
00:24:04,550 --> 00:24:05,650
Kau boleh pergi.

339
00:24:07,410 --> 00:24:08,560
Baik, Bu.

340
00:24:17,530 --> 00:24:19,120
Dia sungguh berpacaran dengan Yeo Jun?

341
00:24:19,200 --> 00:24:20,480
