388
00:27:15,770 --> 00:27:18,060
Aku mencarimu ke mana-mana.

389
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:22,590
Kau merasa amat dicurangi,
tapi kini melakukan hal serupa.

390
00:27:22,990 --> 00:27:24,270
Kau akan seperti Profesor Choi?

391
00:27:25,230 --> 00:27:27,960
Atau ini caramu membalas dendam

392
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:30,210
