393
00:27:31,830 --> 00:27:35,130
Kim So-bin. Kenapa kau membahasnya?

394
00:27:36,370 --> 00:27:38,210
Karena itu pekerjaannya.

395
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:42,040
Aku memeriksa tulisannya
meski hanya berkontribusi membacanya.

396
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:46,090
Serendah itukah pendapatmu tentangku?

397
00:27:47,280 --> 00:27:51,850
Jangan melewati batas, Soo-kyung.

398
00:27:53,000 --> 00:27:54,140
Park Si-jae.

399
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:57,570
Aku bisa mengatakan hal yang sama
dan menutup mulutmu.

400
00:27:58,280 --> 00:27:59,420
