413
00:28:58,070 --> 00:29:00,760
Itu bukan cinta, tapi kebiasaan.

414
00:29:01,510 --> 00:29:03,090
Entah perasaan kita nyata atau tidak,

415
00:29:03,970 --> 00:29:05,860
